title: Lynda - Logic Pro 10.1 New Features
description:
Lynda - Logic Pro 10.1 New Features

Subject:    Audio + Music 
Software:    Logic Pro 
Author:    Scott Hirsch 

54m 26s Appropriate for all Feb 04, 2015 | Uploaded in Apr 26, 2015 by 2boweb

Every new release of Logic is eagerly awaited. But 10.1 is a major leap forward, especially for EDM and hip-hop producers and beat makers. Join Scott Hirsch as he introduces you to the ten new drummers and the new Drum Machine Designer, as well as the improved Retro Synth and the brand-new Mellotron software instrument, powerful new MIDI editing and sequencer features in the revamped Piano Roll Editor, the enhanced Mixer (now with VCA faders and easy viewing of your Track Stack components), real-time fades, and many more enhancements that make Logic Pro 10.1 an instant, must-have upgrade. This course gives you a preview of the new features, as well as shortcuts for integrating them into your production workflow as quickly as possible
